01:02:04,011 --> 01:02:05,096
Because of your face?

1004
01:02:08,349 --> 01:02:09,600
What?

1005
01:02:09,684 --> 01:02:11,519
What's wrong with my face?

1006
01:02:12,103 --> 01:02:13,354
A squid.

1007
01:02:15,898 --> 01:02:17,442
Have some squid.

1008
01:02:17,692 --> 01:02:18,901
-Right.
-Open up.

1009
01:02:20,361 --> 01:02:21,195
Darn it.

1010
01:02:22,238 --> 01:02:24,115
I kind of feel offended.

1011
01:02:26,868 --> 01:02:29,454
Excuse me, Ms. Yun.

1012
01:02:29,871 --> 01:02:32,999
Why did you quit working as a reporter
to do this job?

1013
01:02:35,585 --> 01:02:37,420
Your articles looked great.

1014
01:02:38,629 --> 01:02:40,089
I've read a few.

1015
01:02:40,715 --> 01:02:44,594
I didn't want to write articles anymore.

1016
01:02:46,804 --> 01:02:48,848
The man you saw at the hospital.

1017
01:02:48,931 --> 01:02:50,308
Mr. Shin Jae-gyeong.

1018
01:02:51,893 --> 01:02:53,811
He ended up like that
because of my article.

1019
01:02:57,231 --> 01:02:58,649
-Okay.
-Stop it.

1020
01:02:58,733 --> 01:03:00,651
-More.
-Hey, drink up.

1021
01:03:00,735 --> 01:03:02,111
-Cheers.
-Let's drink until we die.

1022
01:03:02,195 --> 01:03:04,363
-Why did you spill your drink?
-Hey.

1023
01:04:19,564 --> 01:04:21,440
What do you think Mr. Song will say

1024
01:04:21,524 --> 01:04:23,651
if he finds out about
your relationship with Ms. Kang?

1025
01:04:23,734 --> 01:04:26,654
Let's get rid of Oh Won-sik
before Mr. Song's hearing.

1026
01:04:26,737 --> 01:04:27,655
There was an accident

1027
01:04:27,738 --> 01:04:29,448
-at a factory in Seongjin.
-Stop them!

1028
01:04:29,532 --> 01:04:31,742
Don't get intoxicated
with what Mr. Lee has to offer.

1029
01:04:31,826 --> 01:04:34,203
Do you think revealing the truth
will change anything?

1030
01:04:34,287 --> 01:04:36,914
I think Joojin Constructions is
trying to conceal what happened.

1031
01:04:36,998 --> 01:04:39,625
It seems like they made sure
the workers don't talk.

1032
01:04:39,709 --> 01:04:42,253
We need to give up what we're holding
to gain something bigger.

1033
01:04:42,336 --> 01:04:45,548
You're not helping me.
I'm the one who's helping you.

1034
01:04:45,631 --> 01:04:48,509
Do some thinking and decide
what would be a wise move to make.

